Welcome to this audio-visual journey into the fractionalization of the Nftfy logo itself! 

As this marketplace booms, so will the value of this piece!

AI-created and human-curated, Nftfy Fractions is a 1 minute trip into the nature of fractionalization. 

Rainforests.eth always gives half of all sales and royalties to conservation charities, as well as carbon offsetting our wallet monthly. 

Please join us on our journey to bring economic value and real world value of life systems closer together again. WAGMI if the Earth makes it.'}, 'preview_media_file_type2': {'type': 'string', 'description': 'video/mp4'}}
